<h1>Using Cassette in .NET 3.5</h1>

<p>Make sure to use the <code>Cassette.Web.Fx35</code> Nuget package.</p>

<h2>MVC 2 &amp; Web Forms</h2>

<p>For Web Forms, the instructions remain the same.</p>

<p>For MVC2, you must remove the <code>system.web.webPages.razor</code> section from your <code>~/Views/web.config</code> file after installing <strong>Cassette.Views</strong>.</p>

